rules.text: If there are more black than white cats
If there are fewer zoomer cats than fat orange cats
If there are more male calico cats than female calico cats
If there is an outside cat in the bottom left corner
If there are more inside than outside cats
If there is a tabby cat in the bottom right corner
If there is more than 1 muscular Schrodinger cat
If there is a female cat in every corner
If there are more strays than skinny inside cats
If there are more Schrodinger orange than Schrodinger tabby cats
If there are more than two calico cats and today is Sunday
If there are more than 2 stray tabby cats
If the sum of skinny and fat cats is greater than the number of muscular cats
If the sum of inside and stray cats is greater than sum of fat and skinny cats
If there are more female zoomer than male zoomer cats
If the sum of orange and white cats is greater than the number of calico cats
Cool loners! If there are outside cats in every corner
If there is a fat cat in the upper left corner
If there is more than 1 calico female cat and it's Friday
If there are more Millennial than male cats
If there are fewer inside zoomer than outside boomer cats
If there are more muscular than inside cats
Skinny cat Tuesday! If there are at least 5 skinny cats and it is Tuesday
If there are fewer black than boomer cats
If there are more skinny cats than boomer cats
If there are more Schrodinger cats than inside skinny cats
If there is an equal number of female and fat cats
If there are 2 muscular cats and 3 or more white cats
If the number of inside cats is more than the number of fat zoomer cats
If the number of fat inside cats is less than the number of skinny stray cats
If there is an equal number of Schrodinger and white cats
If there is an equal number of female outside and muscular boomer cats
If the bottom row is full of stray cats
If there is at least 1 boomer orange cat
If there is at least one muscular female cat
If there are 2 zoomer cats who are also skinny
If there are more zoomer than boomer cats
If there are more than 2 stray muscular cats and today is Friday
If there is at least 1 millennial black cat
If there is a Schrodinger cat in the middle of the top row
If the sum of stray and outside cats is more than sum of boomer and millennial cats
If the top row is full of millennials
If there is at least 1 female tabby cat
If there are more millennial than orange cats and it's Wednesday
Lonely Lurker! If there is a stray male cat in the upper right corner
If there is at least 1 inside zoomer cat
If the bottom row is full of boomers
If there are fewer than 2 outside fat cats
If there are more than 3 skinny female cats
If there are fewer than 3 muscular white cats
If there is at least 1 white Schrodinger cat
If there are more than three zoomers and it's a Monday
If there are more than 2 cats wearing glasses
If there are more female than male cats
If there is at least 1 outside skinny cat
If there are enough millennial outside cats to fill half the bottom row
